// conformance/59-list-item-action-trailing.ame
// Tests: list_item NORMATIVE nested click target rule (§list_item).
// The row has its own tap action AND a trailing btn with its own action.
// The renderer MUST isolate the trailing tap so it does not also fire the
// row action.
root = list_item("Pizza Place", "71 Mulberry St", icon("restaurant"), btn("Directions", nav("/dir")), action=nav("/detail"))
